storage, will you?

93
00:05:23,421 --> 00:05:26,487
-Oh, uh, OK!

94
00:05:26,521 --> 00:05:29,554
-Just look for the box
labeled "new item," OK?

95
00:05:29,587 --> 00:05:31,021
