101
00:05:45,654 --> 00:05:47,987
-So this is the only
one you could get, then?

102
00:05:48,021 --> 00:05:48,721
-Oh, please.

103
00:05:48,754 --> 00:05:49,954
Give me a break.

104
00:05:49,987 --> 00:05:51,987
