Wasn't all that easy to come by.

106
00:05:53,421 --> 00:05:54,087
Now, look.

107
00:05:56,721 --> 00:05:57,787
Just go easy.

108
00:05:57,821 --> 00:06:01,287
You can't fake it
forever, all right?

109
00:06:01,321 --> 00:06:02,487
-Yes, I know that.

110
00:06:07,721 --> 00:06:09,854
-Good morning!
[giggle] Hi, everyone.

111
00:06:09,887 --> 00:06:10,954
How are you?

112
00:06:10,987 --> 00:06:11,454
-Huh?

113
00:06:11,487 --> 00:06:11,954
-Oh.

114
00:06:11,987 --> 00:06:12,621
Hey.

115
00:06:12,654 --> 00:06:13,654
