RUKIA (OFFSCREEN): Oh,
Ichigo, what just happened?

125
00:06:31,887 --> 00:06:34,354
I better get you to
the nurse's office.

126
00:06:34,387 --> 00:06:37,621
-She, uh, just hit
him, didn't she?

127
00:06:37,654 --> 00:06:39,321
-I didn't see a thing.

128
00:06:39,354 --> 00:06:40,754
RUKIA (OFFSCREEN): Here.

129
00:06:40,787 --> 00:06:42,621
-What's this supposed to be?

130
