and a substitute soul

134
00:06:50,221 --> 00:06:53,121
will enter the body, so
the real one can roam free.

135
00:06:53,154 --> 00:06:55,521
If the time comes that
you must face a Hollow

136
00:06:55,554 --> 00:06:57,287
and I'm not around,
you can use them

137
00:06:57,321 --> 00:06:59,687
to transform into a Soul Reaper.

138
00:06:59,721 --> 00:07:02,221
-It's got "Soul Candy"
printed right on here.

139
00:07:02,254 --> 00:07:03,454
-Oh.

140
00:07:03,487 --> 00:07:05,687
That's only because the
Soul Society Women's League

141
00:07:05,721 --> 00:07:06,721
