that one, all right?

148
00:07:16,021 --> 00:07:19,621
I asked for Chappy the Rabbit.

149
00:07:19,654 --> 00:07:20,754
-OK.

150
00:07:20,787 --> 00:07:23,121
So you wanted one shaped
like a rabbit then, huh?

151
00:07:23,154 --> 00:07:23,821
-What's that?

152
