What did you just say?

153
00:07:25,487 --> 00:07:27,121
How dare you mock
me, you imbecile!

154
00:07:27,154 --> 00:07:28,854
-It's not that.

155
00:07:28,887 --> 00:07:31,954
I just didn't understand
your explanation is all.

156
00:07:31,987 --> 00:07:32,921
-Go ahead.

157
00:07:32,954 --> 00:07:34,787
Swallow one, and
it'll all be clear.

158
00:07:53,454 --> 00:07:54,387
-Huh?

159
00:07:54,421 --> 00:07:55,987
