160
00:07:56,021 --> 00:07:58,121
-Oh, don't be so shocked.

161
00:07:58,154 --> 00:07:59,987
Inside that empty
shelf of a body

162
00:08:00,021 --> 00:08:02,254
there resides a substitute soul.

163
00:08:02,287 --> 00:08:07,521
And no one will even notice
that your true soul is gone.

164
00:08:07,554 --> 00:08:08,021
-What?

165
00:08:11,354 --> 00:08:11,921
-Hi.

166
00:08:11,954 --> 00:08:13,221
Good afternoon.

167
00:08:13,254 --> 00:08:14,087
Nice to meet you.

168
00:08:14,121 --> 00:08:14,921
I'm Ichigo Kurosaki.

169
00:08:17,221 --> 00:08:18,621
Early to bed, early to rise.

170
00:08:18,654 --> 00:08:20,087
That's my motto.

171
00:08:20,121 --> 00:08:22,254
-Early to bed, early to what?

172
00:08:22,287 --> 00:08:23,754
-It's pretty amazing, isn't it?

173
00:08:23,787 --> 00:08:25,454
-Amazing, my ass!

174
00:08:25,487 --> 00:08:26,854
What is that thing over there?

175
00:08:26,887 --> 00:08:29,187
How can he be me if I'm me?

176
00:08:29,221 --> 00:08:30,087
[beeping]

177
00:08:30,121 --> 00:08:31,821
-Hm?

178
00:08:31,854 --> 00:08:33,021
Perfect timing.

179
00:08:33,054 --> 00:08:34,354
