Are-- are you deranged?

182
00:08:38,154 --> 00:08:38,721
RUKIA (OFFSCREEN): Let's go!

183
00:08:38,754 --> 00:08:39,521
-No way.

184
00:08:39,554 --> 00:08:40,854
They'll know he's a fake.

185
00:08:40,887 --> 00:08:41,821
Hey, you!

186
00:08:41,854 --> 00:08:44,054
Make sure you attend
my next class.

187
00:08:44,087 --> 00:08:45,387
-[laughs] Don't worry.

188
00:08:45,421 --> 00:08:46,921
Leave everything to me, Master.

189
00:08:50,087 --> 00:08:51,054
Take your time.

190
00:08:54,687 --> 00:08:55,354
-Wait a sec.

191
00:08:58,254 --> 00:08:59,721
Oh, man.

192
00:08:59,754 --> 00:09:01,387
JINTA (OFFSCREEN):
Take a good look!

193
00:09:01,421 --> 00:09:02,287
What does it say?

194
00:09:02,321 --> 00:09:03,054
Go on.

195
00:09:03,087 --> 00:09:03,854
Read it.

196
00:09:03,887 --> 00:09:06,287
-Uh, "Defective Goods"?

197
00:09:06,321 --> 00:09:07,254
-Yeah, that's right.

198
00:09:07,287 --> 00:09:08,287
Defective goods.

199
00:09:08,321 --> 00:09:10,354
Do you have any idea
what you've done?

200
00:09:10,387 --> 00:09:13,287
You sold a customer faulty
merchandise, you dummy!

201
00:09:13,321 --> 00:09:14,054
-Oh.

202
00:09:14,087 --> 00:09:14,887
-Moron!

203
00:09:14,921 --> 00:09:16,754
Get your act together, will you?

204
00:09:16,787 --> 00:09:18,454
