207
00:09:19,987 --> 00:09:21,087
No fighting.

208
00:09:21,121 --> 00:09:23,787
-You know, if we're not
careful, this gikongan

209
00:09:23,821 --> 00:09:25,454
could cause some real problems.

210
00:09:25,487 --> 00:09:26,654
-You got that right.

211
00:09:26,687 --> 00:09:28,087
We can't just sit on this.

212
00:09:28,121 --> 00:09:30,487
We better take care
of it right away.

213
00:09:30,521 --> 00:09:32,121
