what he might do

214
00:09:32,154 --> 00:09:33,954
if we let him run
loose out there.

215
00:09:55,321 --> 00:09:55,954
-All right.

216
00:09:55,987 --> 00:09:57,654
Feeling pretty good.

217
00:09:57,687 --> 00:10:01,121
Been too long since I had
a body to get around in.

218
00:10:01,154 --> 00:10:03,121
Looks like I'm finally free.

219
00:10:03,154 --> 00:10:05,787
-Hey, what are you doing there?

220
00:10:05,821 --> 00:10:07,087
Hm.

221
00:10:07,121 --> 00:10:09,521
Aren't you Kurosaki from the
ninth grade, group three?

222
00:10:09,554 --> 00:10:11,221
What have you been doing here?

223
00:10:11,254 --> 00:10:13,121
And why is that
fence all busted up?

224
00:10:22,854 --> 00:10:23,521
Huh?

225
00:10:23,554 --> 00:10:24,354
What's with that look?

226
00:10:26,854 --> 00:10:30,054
[gasp] Huh?

227
00:10:30,087 --> 00:10:33,121
He-- he leaped to there?

228
00:10:33,154 --> 00:10:35,321
-[laughs] Surprise,
surprise, old man.

229
00:10:41,154 --> 00:10:44,021
[school bell]

230
00:10:44,054 --> 00:10:44,987
-All right!

231
00:10:45,021 --> 00:10:47,287
At last, time for lurch!

232
00:10:47,321 --> 00:10:47,921
-Jeez, Orihime.

233
00:10:47,954 --> 00:10:48,987
