234
00:10:49,021 --> 00:10:51,387
It's not a big deal.

235
00:10:51,421 --> 00:10:53,321
-How can you say that, Tatsuki?

236
00:10:53,354 --> 00:10:55,554
Everyone knows that a healthy,
red-blooded high school

237
00:10:55,587 --> 00:10:58,921
girl comes to school for only
one reason-- to eat her lunch.

238
00:10:58,954 --> 00:10:59,821
-Yeah, yeah.

239
00:10:59,854 --> 00:11:00,487
I get it.

240
00:11:00,521 --> 00:11:01,821
Have a seat already.

241
00:11:01,854 --> 00:11:04,054
-So, Tatsuki, what do
you have for lunch today?

242
00:11:04,087 --> 00:11:06,087
I've got bread and
red bean paste.

243
00:11:06,121 --> 00:11:07,254
-That sounds good.

244
00:11:07,287 --> 00:11:09,521
Unfortunately, my lunch
is a little more ordinary.

245
00:11:09,554 --> 00:11:10,554
ORIHIME (OFFSCREEN): See?

246
00:11:10,587 --> 00:11:12,454
I can make my own red bean buns.

247
00:11:12,487 --> 00:11:14,121
TATSUKI (OFFSCREEN):
Interesting choice.

248
00:11:14,154 --> 00:11:17,554
-Orihime, why don't
you and I eat together?

249
00:11:17,587 --> 00:11:19,221
-Um, yeah.

250
00:11:19,254 --> 00:11:20,121
OK.

251
00:11:20,154 --> 00:11:22,121
[giggle]

252
00:11:22,154 --> 00:11:23,587
-That's so cute!

253
00:11:23,621 --> 00:11:27,154
You bite into an entire
loaf of bread and smile

254
00:11:27,187 --> 00:11:28,487
with crumbs all over your mouth.

255
00:11:32,921 --> 00:11:33,354
-[gasp]

256
00:11:33,387 --> 00:11:34,421
-'Scuze me.

257
00:11:34,454 --> 00:11:37,287
This is the ninth grade,
class group, right?

258
00:11:37,321 --> 00:11:44,854
-[shouts]

259
00:11:50,754 --> 00:11:52,387
-Man, I'm getting a bad feeling.

260
00:12:05,469 --> 00:12:06,803
-What-- wait a second!

261
00:12:06,836 --> 00:12:08,603
How the hell did you
get up here like that?

262
00:12:08,636 --> 00:12:10,336
-What do you mean, how?

263
00:12:10,369 --> 00:12:11,836
I jumped up here.

264
00:12:11,869 --> 00:12:14,403
You saw it with your
